title: Carl Cox - All Roads Lead To The Dancefloor (The Remixes)
description: 2013 has seen Carl Cox's & Jon Rundell's seminal label Intec return to the worlds stage. Theyve spent the year building their roster, discovering underground talent, launching a new series of club nights across Europe, and all the while continuing to dominate with some of the years best new releases.  One of the biggest of the year, came in April with the long awaited Pure Intec compilation series, Pure Intec Two released 9 years after the hugely successful original Pure Intec.  Part 1 was mixed by Carl himself, a collection of unheard remixes from his acclaimed album, All Roads Lead to The Dancefloor, whilst Part 2 came courtesy of Jon Rundell and featured brand new tracks from some of Intecs finest DJs. Those that have already listened to Carls Pure Intec 2 CD will be familiar with the mixes from Carls "All Roads Leads To The Dancefloor." But now for the first time ever theyll have the chance to buy remixes from the likes of Loco Dice, Joel Mull, Ben Sims, Guti, Yousef, Tomy DeClerque,... as individual downloads.  Enjoy !
